DOC.brief_summary: To collect the outcome of frozen-thawed embryo transfer cycles after the embryos are cryopreserved up to at least 1 year in Trial P05787 (NCT00696800), in order to estimate the cumulative pregnancy rate for each treatment group.
DOC.brief_title: Follow-up Study of Frozen-thawed Embryo Transfer (FTET) Cycles After Cryopreservation of Embryos in Clinical Trial P05787 (P05716)
DOC.detailed_description: This is a follow-up protocol to collect the outcome of frozen-thawed embryo transfer cycles, performed after the embryos are cryopreserved up to at least 1 year in Trial P05787 (NCT00696800), to enable estimation of the cumulative pregnancy rate for each treatment group.
DOC.criteria: Participants from whom embryos have been cryopreserved in Base Trial P05787 (NCT00696800), of which at least one embryo is thawed for use in a subsequent FTET cycle; Able and willing to give informed consent.
